  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare and evaluate the pharmacokinetic characteristics and
      the safety of varespladib methyl in mild or moderate renal impairment patients and healthy
      volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
